Note:
data/serde/xml/core/parser.runa
XML Parser Framework

This module provides comprehensive XML parsing capabilities including
SAX (event-driven) parsing, DOM (tree-based) parsing, XML document
validation, encoding support, and advanced parsing features.
:End Note

Import "dev/debug/errors/core" as Errors

